The paper deals with the interpretability of convolutional neural networks (CNN's) and their ability to generalize to unseen data. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and possibly social and information networks (cs.SI) due to the use of topological data analysis.
